h red chairs and patterned napkins.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-4-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-4-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-4-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-4-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560953\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560953\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with blue cabinets, white countertops, and pendant lights. Includes a central island, red stool, and shelves with various items. Bright, natural light streams through the window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-5-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560954\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560954\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-6-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen with blue cabinets, white countertops, and open wooden shelves holding plants and dishes. A stove with a blue pot is centered under a range hood.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-6-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-6-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560955\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560955\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with blue cabinets, white countertops, and a white island sink. Open shelves display dishes. Window above main sink, red wall lights, and potted plants as decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYellow, requested by the client’s eldest child, Vincent, became a key inspiration throughout the design (check out the yellow bathtub below!). The challenge lay in using this vivid color without overpowering the overall palette, and Pigliacampo’s approach succeeded in bringing in warmth and energy, while keeping the design cohesive.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560956\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560956\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-8-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with a white island, blue cabinet, and yellow lower cabinets. A checkered rug leads to an open door, with plants and shelves adding decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-8-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-8-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560957\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560957\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home bar with wooden shelves displaying bottles and glasses, a small fridge, a blue accent wall, and a red pendant light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe project also embraced practical, cost-effective strategies, such as refinishing the original hardwood floors with a sheer white stain to neutralize their yellow tone and updating the carpeted bedrooms with matching wood flooring. Pigliacampo and her contractor repurposed cabinetry in the kitchen, playroom, mudroom, and primary bedroom, saving on material costs while preserving quality.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560958\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560958\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-10-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Bright open kitchen and dining area with large windows, red chairs around a table, plants, and modern decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-10-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-10-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560959\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560959\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Room with geometric floor tiles, blue cabinets, an orange bench, and colorful decor. Wall art includes a Bauhaus poster. A small window and indoor plants are present.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDespite Pigliacampo’s physical distance from the project, with her being up to 17 hours away at times, the renovation was completed with impressive craftsmanship thanks to a dedicated contractor and collaborative tradespeople. Some of the design elements were new to the team, including the use of tambour and concrete skim materials, but these were executed successfully, adding unique textures and finishes to the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560960\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560960\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A bathroom features a round mirror, geometric gray tiles, a yellow sink with two knobs, a white faucet, a hanging bulb, and a purple and white patterned towel. A plant is on the left.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560961\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560961\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with a wall-mounted art collection, plants, a colorful rug, and a staircase. A dark sideboard sits beneath the artwork.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne of the more unexpected challenges in the project came from updating the home’s outdated technology. The existing lighting and sound system, state-of-the-art when installed in 2007, required a substantial investment to integrate with the new fixtures and design changes. This experience left Pigliacampo with a cautionary lesson about the risks of embedding too much technology in a home’s infrastructure, which can quickly become obsolete.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560962\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560962\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a white staircase, art on the walls, and plants. A black cabinet with decor underneath a loft area with chairs and a plant. Natural light fills the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560963\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560963\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A modern room with a dark armchair, a small side table, and a checkered rug. Three windows offer a view of trees and mountains. A bookshelf with plants stands near the corner.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe finished home now reflects a blend of the client’s love for bold colors and Pigliacampo’s clever design ideas. The use of Schoolhouse Electric and Dutton Brown lighting, Fireclay and Florida tiles, and custom furniture pieces like the striking Vitra chair in the living room, all contribute to the home’s modern yet personalized feel. Ultimately, this project exemplifies how thoughtful collaboration and creative reuse of materials can result in a home that feels both fresh and familiar.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560964\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560964\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A bright bedroom with bunk beds, a colorful striped blanket, and a tall shelf of stacked books by the window. A globe and framed poster sit on a dresser. A yellow phone is on a nightstand.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560965\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560965\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-17-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with blue tiled walls, round mirror, light wood vanity, plants, and colorful decor, including a red stool and a yellow patterned rug.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-17-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-17-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.c