ants. A framed artwork is displayed above the tub.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-23-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-23-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560972\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560972\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with a vibrant yellow bathtub, potted plants, a patterned towel, and framed artwork on the ledge.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560973\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560973\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Durango-Colorado-House-Amy-Pigliacampo-25-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with an oval mirror, green tiled backsplash, marble countertop, beige vanity, potted plant, and wall light. To